## Backups

Off-site copies go to {{backups.destination}}, in private, File Lock-protected
buckets (immutable for the retention window below, with older versions pruned
after the lifecycle window).

{{#each backups.buckets}}
{{#if sync}}
`{{sync.source}}` is pushed there {{cronToHuman sync.schedule.minute sync.schedule.hour sync.schedule.dom sync.schedule.month sync.schedule.dow}}
via TrueNAS CloudSync ({{sync.direction}}/{{sync.transferMode}}), with a
{{retentionDays}}-day File Lock retention and a {{lifecycleDeleteDays}}-day
lifecycle prune.
{{else}}
The second bucket, `{{name}}`, holds the same {{retentionDays}}-day File Lock /
{{lifecycleDeleteDays}}-day lifecycle protection, but is replicated by Garage
itself rather than through a Pulumi-managed CloudSync task.
{{/if}}
{{/each}}
{{#if notBackedUpPools}}
{{humanList notBackedUpPools}} {{#if (isSingular notBackedUpPools)}}isn't{{else}}aren't{{/if}} included in this off-site sync.
{{/if}}

